                <h3 class="subheading">Design: The Art of Escapism and a Global Nod of Approval</h3>


                <p>The design philosophy guiding the new Sierra is fundamentally about daring to escape the ordinary, and the world has already taken notice. The Sierra’s ground-breaking aesthetic was crowned the <span class="font-weight-700">Red Dot Winner 2025,</span> one of the most prestigious design competitions globally. This iconic feat, being the first car in India to be recognized by Red Dot, establishes the Sierra as an SUV that truly redefines possibilities.</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">Exterior Excellence: Modernity Meets Heritage</span></p>
