                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center image-height"><img src="~/images/blogs/2025/nov/tata sierra2025/header.webp" alt="header" title="header" loading="lazy" /></div>
                </div>

                <p>The exterior styling masterfully blends the boxy, authoritative silhouette of the original with contemporary, cutting-edge elements.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Signature Lighting: </span>The front fascia is dominated by the expansive <span class="font-weight-700">LIGHT SABER LED DRLS</span> (Daytime Running Lights) that stretch across the width of the vehicle, offering a dramatic welcome and goodbye light signature to greet the owner in style. Below these DRLs sit the<span class="font-weight-700"> NIGHT SABER BI-LED BOOSTER HEADLAMPS,</span> which are designed to be bright, focused, and ready to take on the night with powerful illumination. Further enhancing visibility are the <span class="font-weight-700">Front Fog Lamps with Cornering Function.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">A Nod to the Past: </span>The Sierra retains its unmistakable identity through the signature <span class="font-weight-700">Wrap-Around Glass Effect </span>(the iconic Alpine window). While reimagined for the modern era, the high-set bonnet, squarish wheel arches, and thick B-pillar ensure a strong connection to its 1990s predecessor.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Contemporary Touches:</span> Adding to the sleek, uncluttered look are <span class="font-weight-700">Flush Door Handles with Welcome Lights,</span> a feature typically found on high-end luxury vehicles. The SUV rides on imposing <span class="font-weight-700">R19 Alloy Wheels, </span>which are among the largest in the segment, giving it a confident and upright stance with undeniable road presence. The practicality is boosted by a <span class="font-weight-700">Powered Tailgate with Gesture Control, </span>making loading and unloading effortless. The overall look is completed by a stylish <span class="font-weight-700">Dual Tone Roof </span>and modern <span class="font-weight-700">Sequential Indicators</span>.</li>
                </ul>

                <p>
                    <span class="font-weight-700">A Sanctuary on Wheels: Interior Features and Ultimate Comfort</span>
                </p>
