                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Audio and Air: </span>The acoustic experience is top-tier, thanks to the <span class="font-weight-700">Theater Pro with 12 JBL Black Speaker Setup powered by Dolby Atmos, </span>delivering immersive 3D sound—a feature none of its primary rivals offer. Cabin air quality is maintained by the<span class="font-weight-700"> BreatheIQ Purifier with AQI Display, </span>ensuring the air is always clean and healthy.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Seating and Ergonomics: </span>The SUV offers premium <span class="font-weight-700">Ventilated Seats </span>for maximum comfort in diverse climates. The driver benefits from a<span class="font-weight-700"> 6-Way Powered Driver Seat with Memory & Welcome</span> function, which adjusts the seat automatically for ease of entry/exit and recalls personalized driving profiles. For rear-seat passengers, comfort is prioritized with a unique <span class="font-weight-700">Rear Seat with 2-Stage Recline function and the Boss Mode</span> lever, allowing them to adjust the front passenger seat for maximum legroom.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Adding to the long list of amenities are dual<span class="font-weight-700"> USB C+C 65W chargers </span>for fast device charging, a <span class="font-weight-700">Wireless Charger, </span>and a practical <span class="font-weight-700">Cooled Glovebox. </span>The Sierra also boasts a segment-leading<span class="font-weight-700"> Boot Space</span> of 622 Litres, which expands to a massive 1257 Litres with the rear seats folded, catering perfectly to long-distance travelers and families.</p>
